All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class BeanFormRow<K,R>
extends FormRow<K,R>

Represents one editable row that is a bean of type R. The form row has a key of type K. A BeanFormListWidget may contain multiple rows but all of them have common row key and row data types.

Since:
2.0

Martti Tamm (martti@araneaframework.org)
